Privacy Policy for "WiFi Info" Mobile Application
Effective Date: [11-1-2025]

Introduction
Welcome to "WiFi Info”, The Application developed by us,"Eng.Mohamed”. We take your privacy seriously and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data when you use our mobile application. By downloading, installing, or using the App, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:
1-	Personal Information: We do not collect personal information such as your name, address, phone number, or email address when you use the App.
2 - Non-Personal Information:
o	Device Information: We do not collect device-specific information, including the type of device you use, unique device identifiers, operating system version.
o	Networke Information: We get mobile network information(wifi network name, ip address,netmask, gateway, dns servers, dhcp server) for display ONLY.
o	Gameplay Data: We do not collect information related to your interactions with the App, including game progress, scores, and preferences (in this release of Application).
o	Technical Information: We may automatically collect technical information such as app crashes, error reports, and usage patterns.

Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not share any of your information with third parties. 

Data Security
We don’t have any stored data (in this release of Application) to be secured. 

Children's Privacy
The App is designed for children and adults and complies with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA). We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13 without parental consent. If you believe that we have unintentionally collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us, and we will promptly take appropriate action.

Third-Party Services
The App may include third-party services or links to third-party websites (Ads). These third parties may have their own privacy policies and practices. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third parties but we controlled and blocked any sensitive contents (Astrology & Esoteric, Cosmetic Procedures & Body Modification, Dating, Drugs & Supplements, Politics, References to Sex, Religion, Sensationalism, Sexual & Reproductive Health, Significant Skin Exposure, Social Casino Games, Weight Loss).

Your Rights and Choices
•	Access and Deletion: You may request access to the data we have collected about you and request its deletion.
•	Data Portability: You can request to receive a copy of your data in a structured, commonly used, and machine-readable format.
•	Opt-Out: You can opt-out of certain data collection by disabling specific permissions on your device or discontinuing the use of the App.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our data practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the App. We recommend reviewing this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

Contact Us
